{"tid":2495390,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"熊黛林孖女三歲生日影Cute爆寫真　盡得母親遺傳勁識擺Post","createTime":"2021-04-19T07:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T11:36:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"65699a01266b73393ede609dcd514554ba378014","tid":2495390,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"藝人熊黛林（Lynn）自2016年與藝人郭可盈的弟弟郭可頌結婚，兩年後誕下雙胞胎女兒Kaylor與Lyvia。轉眼孖女已經3歲，今天（19日）Lynn在IG發布多張女兒們的照片，並寫道：「孖寶三歲了」。<br />\n<br />\n照片中姊妹二人長大了很多，雖然只有三歲，但已有女神風範，Cute爆模樣深受網友喜愛。重點是這輯三歲生日照片中，完全展露孖女遺傳了Lynn的模特兒基因，懂得做各種各樣的姿勢，獲網友大讚：「已經係專業模特兒」、「童年版Lynn」、「真係好可愛」、「大個咗好多，有女神味道」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210321/450309957976330240435862.jpeg/PJDqd6DudpWEbbfdPignPsSSCQ10bVEMOkRSrjpEUq4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210321%2F450309957976330240435862.jpeg%2FPJDqd6DudpWEbbfdPignPsSSCQ10bVEMOkRSrjpEUq4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=abc3c690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210321/450305652875595776602714.jpeg/b7CUlxLIC3h-5M8nFm1Iu_Ps1LeUw0AoRZ3PTkWdz04?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210321%2F450305652875595776602714.jpeg%2Fb7CUlxLIC3h-5M8nFm1Iu_Ps1LeUw0AoRZ3PTkWdz04%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ced57d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460796106603761664198240.png/dqWge1hnVFWAML2RxmcLUILu-cydXG3GxXYhCcV2IQk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460796106603761664198240.png%2FdqWge1hnVFWAML2RxmcLUILu-cydXG3GxXYhCcV2IQk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dde8227f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460796112316665856290875.png/0tR6bjVP2KYsLSLT1oMv4A9L0liVpX4cn-HNk5_hzZM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk